{"tid":539551,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"智識加 真係小學生最佳讀物","createTime":"2018-01-24T15:42:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T15:47:37.000Z","uid":139716,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9974209079aa2037ee8c0f29bbb59a051c8b89f5","tid":539551,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:42:02.000Z","msg":"中西飲食文化差異係<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n...<br />\n西方人 <br />\nIt tastes amazing！ <br />\nIt&amp;amp;#039;s good. <br />\nThis food is FXCKING yummy. <br />\n如果他有點知識水平的話，評語就會變成這樣. . . <br />\nOH~我的腦中充滿了多巴胺和血清素，這種感覺好像戀愛般那樣的romantic啊！ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n東方人 <br />\n老闆煮的這碗刀削麵吃起來Q中又帶有嚼勁(此字要發捲舌音，才能重現當時的意境)，好像在我的舌頭上跳舞般那樣的彈牙啊！ <br />\n這家店的豆花在糖水與配料的互相調合之下，就好像劉關張他們桃園三結義一樣缺一不可啊！而入口即化的那種綿密口感彷彿回到媽媽的懷裡，充滿了無法形容的安全感，這真是人間極品啊！ <br />\n從來未試過如此清新、脫俗的感覺，牛肉的鮮、瀨尿蝦的甜，摻在一起的味道，居然比老鼠斑有過之而無不及，甚至比我的初戀更加詩情畫意，所謂「舉頭望明月，低頭思故鄉」，好詩！好詩！ <br />\n啊娘喂~這真是夭壽好吃的啦！我要趕快通知火旺、罔市、志明、春嬌他們一起來好好品嘗一下，這樣氣氛才會HIGH啊！"},{"pid":"825c083a3d313b8632203798bc4b9352402ce7fb","tid":539551,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:42:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20090930000016KK08537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.answers.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Findex%3Fqid%3D20090930000016KK08537&d=w1QEDnFPI8RY27QzDYX3Yf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=55dda719\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20090930000016KK08537</a>"},{"pid":"4566cf6876793f45eb3ced1619490c985ad51ae9","tid":539551,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T15:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297d6ebf1d676cf80e57b6861da13eabbad5c8c4","tid":539551,"uid":139716,"like":0,"dislike":